Usage: specify_cell_stack_area [-help] -cell <string> -group <string>
                               -rect {x1 y1 x2 y2}

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
-cell <string>          # specify the cell name (string, required)
-group <string>         # specify the group name (string, required)
-rect {x1 y1 x2 y2}     # specify the constraint rectangular area
                        # (box, required)